<div><head>證俗音</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-1a.2">今謂女嫁後三日餉食為餪女。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-1a.3">南方謂凝牛、羊、鹿血為䘓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-1a.4">以虀噉之消酒。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-1a.5">炙去毛為燂。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-1a.6">𪍴𪍣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-1a.7">內國呼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-1a.8">為環，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-1a.9">亦餅呼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-1a.10">寒具。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-2a.2">今江南呼饊飯己煎米，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-2a.3">以糖餅之者為粰𥹷也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-2a.4">音浮流。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-2a.5">葖蘆菔蕪菁屬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-2a.6">紫花大根，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-2a.7">俗呼為雹葖。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-2a.8">氍&amp;CH-0F01C9;，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-2a.9">毛席也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-3a.2">赨蛇肉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-3a.3">食之辟蠱毒。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-3a.4">蝘蜓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-3a.5">山東謂之𧋐𧐎，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-3a.6">音七錫、名敵反。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-3a.7">陜以西謂之壁宮。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-3a.8">蝤蛑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-3a.9">大蟹也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-3a.10">音在侯、莫侯二反。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-4a.2">有毛者曰蟚蜞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-4a.3">無毛者為彭螖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-4a.4">堪食，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-4a.5">俗呼彭越，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-4a.6">訛耳。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-4a.7">鰿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-4a.8">吳人呼為鯽魚。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2f1227_CHANT_001-4a.9">並《北戶錄注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
